Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:71601,75939}{\i1}September 2, 1870.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:75939,79509}{\i1}Prussian troops defeated\Nthe French army in Sedan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:79509,81978}{\i1}and began to march\Nto the French capital, Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:81978,84548}{\i1}The danger was imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:90720,92789}{\i1}Do you expect us to die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:92789,95058}{\i1}We're going back to protect Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95058,96793}{\i1}We still have Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120116,121418}We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121418,122852}This is Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122852,123753}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123753,126623}It's the lights of Paris.\NWe're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127457,128191}Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128191,131328}This is Captain Andréa.\NThis man needs immediate medical help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131328,131962}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138702,141171}Life's full of irony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141171,143540}Just a moment\Nafter we made it…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144608,145742}Andréa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147043,148345}Is that you, Andréa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148345,149679}Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151047,152182}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152549,154017}Andréa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154017,154985}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154985,156252}Andréa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156252,157854}I knew you'd be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158121,161891}You're a man that\Nwill not go down so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161891,163493}I'm glad to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163760,166529}As long as I have Paris,\NI will not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166529,169432}I won't give Paris to Prussia,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169432,172535}I came back\Nto defend our capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172869,175605}Let's defend it together.\NThis is our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176006,178441}The honor of France is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178441,179442}Let's do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180610,182278}I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183179,184581}With the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184581,185682}Yeah.
